bsp;  *<br> <br>Now, let us remember one basic thing. Soul in us,=
 mind in us, energy in us,
 learning spirit in us, wisdom in us, happiness =
in us, discipline/patience in us - all these are different manifestations o=
f the same Self. However, when Self manifests as these different aspects, i=
t has different qualities and plays different roles. There is no comparison=
 between them.<br> <br>We MAY focus on one aspect of us first, perfect=
 it and then perfect other aspects through it. But, we need balance between=
 all aspects in the end. Similarly, these different aspects of Supreme Bein=
g are incomparable and are in a balance working together in the Cosmos.<br>=
 <br>*        *   &n=
bsp;    *<br> <br>One who is fascinated by the qualitie=
s of soul may like the story that demonstrates how soul operates; one who i=
